An diugh an Aona ’s cha chluinn iad sinn.'</p></td>
<td data-valign="top"><p> </p></td>
<td data-valign="top"><p>The tribe of the green mantles,<br />
And of the hillocks reposeful and smooth,<br />
The blessing of the spell (?) and of the travelling be theirs--<br />
To-day is Friday and they cannot hear us.</p></td>
